  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1962 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">In the upper section, the framed leaflet displays the film title in Serbo-Croatian: ‘Dve sedmice u drugom gradu’ (in the English original: ‘Two Weeks in Another Town’). The title is printed in bright letters on a black background. The rest of the leaflet features a photograph of a man and a woman. The man is older than the woman and has dark hair. He is wearing a striped jacket, a dark necktie and a white shirt. The woman has dark hair and is wearing a white low-cut dress. They are close, with his right hand touching her left shoulder while her hands rest on his chest.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The film was directed by Vincente Minnelli and released in 1962.</ab>
